    m_Localized: ORACLE
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25083740377415683
    m_Localized: "Les Lignes de Force sont align\xE9es."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25083740377415684
    m_Localized: "L'\xE9ther est turbulent ici. Essayez un autre endroit."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25083740377415685
    m_Localized: "En attente du souffle sacr\xE9..."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25083740377415686
    m_Localized: Commencement du Rituel du Visage.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25083740377415687
    m_Localized: "Le chemin de l'ombre r\xE9v\xE8le votre v\xE9ritable essence."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25083740377415688
    m_Localized: Royaume Inconnu
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25083740377415689
    m_Localized: "Votre h\xE9ritage reste \xE0 \xE9crire..."
