    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25636971612569604
    m_Localized: "Le seuil de l'\xE9ternit\xE9 attend votre pr\xE9sence."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25636971612569605
    m_Localized: En attente de l'authentification de l'utilisateur.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25636971612569606
    m_Localized: La porte est ouverte, entre !
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25636971616763904
    m_Localized: ATTENTE_HANDSHAKE_CLIENT...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25636971620958208
    m_Localized: "Le chemin n\xE9cessite une vibration plus profonde..."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25636971620958209
    m_Localized: "Entr\xE9e invalide. Longueur minimale non atteinte."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25636971620958210
    m_Localized: Oups, trop court ! Ajoute d'autres chiffres.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25636971620958211
    m_Localized: "ERR_LONGUEUR_ENTR\xC9E_INSUFFISANTE"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25636971620958212
    m_Localized: "INVOCATION DE LA SYM\xC9TRIE..."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25636971620958213
    m_Localized: "CONNEXION AU R\xC9SEAU..."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25636971620958214
    m_Localized: Attends un peu, on y est presque...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25636971620958215
    m_Localized: INITIALISATION_SERVICES_CENTRAUX...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25636971620958216
    m_Localized: "Les \xE9toiles sont d\xE9salign\xE9es. R\xE9essayez."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25636971620958217
    m_Localized: "La connexion a \xE9chou\xE9. Veuillez r\xE9essayer."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25636971620958218
    m_Localized: "Quelque chose s'est mal pass\xE9. R\xE9essaie !"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25636971620958219
    m_Localized: TIMEOUT_HANDSHAKE
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25636971620958220
    m_Localized: Le fil cosmique a rompu. Reconnectez-vous.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25636971620958221
    m_Localized: "Erreur critique. Contactez le support ou r\xE9essayez."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25636971620958222
    m_Localized: "Gros bug ici ! R\xE9essaie encore une fois."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25636971620958223
    m_Localized: "EXCEPTION_CRITIQUE_SYST\xC8ME"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25636971650318336
    m_Localized: "R\xE9sonance d'\xE2me dans l'\xE9ther."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25636971650318337
    m_Localized: "Attente du souffle sacr\xE9..."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25636971654512640
    m_Localized: Initialisation du protocole...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25636971654512641
    m_Localized: "Attends, je v\xE9rifie..."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
